title: Dwight Slade
description: Dwight Slade (Comedy! AMERICAN: The Bill Hicks Story) is an amazing man and a lifelong friend and comedy partner of the legendary Bill Hicks. But beyond that, Dwight is a hilarious and incredible person and one of Pete's oldest friend in comedy. Please enjoy, you weird weirdos!
